                    "value": "<p>A wrath riot thrives on mayhem, and when members of the throng find themselves facing moments of calm, however brief or temporary, the throng suffers. Whenever the wrath riot fails a saving throw against an affect that would normally @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Fascinated]{Fascinate}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Fatigued]{Fatigue}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Paralyzed]{Paralyze}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Restrained]{Restrain}, or @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Slowed]{Slow} at least four creatures, the troop takes [[/r (3d6+10)[mental]]] damage.</p>"
