                    "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per round</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The throng furiously tears at each enemy within its squares and within 5 feet (@Check[type:reflex|dc:37] save). Damage depends on the number of actions.</p>\n<p><span class=\"pf2-icon\">1</span> Damage [[/r (1d12+14)[slashing],1d6[evil]]]{1d12+14 slashing plus 1d6 evil}</p>\n<p><span class=\"pf2-icon\">2</span> Damage [[/r (2d12+14)[slashing],1d6[evil]]]{2d12+14 slashing plus 1d6 evil}</p>\n<p><span class=\"pf2-icon\">3</span> Damage [[/r (3d12+14)[slashing],1d6[evil]]]{3d12+14 slashing plus 1d6 evil}</p>"
