                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>A wrath riot is less organized and more vicious than most troops. They can move into other creatures' spaces, and other creatures can move into their spaces. Their spaces are difficult terrain to non-demon creatures. The first time during a turn that a creature hostile to the throng willingly moves into their space, that creature is subjected to the one-action version of Beaks, Claws, and Talons.</p>"
